law.text: Nothing in this chapter shall supersede KRS 156.010 nor shall any fee be required for any student enrolling in a program operated by either the State Board for Occupational Education or the State Department of Education.
law.history: Amended 1980 Ky. Acts ch. 188, sec. 260, effective July 15, 1980. -- Amended 1978 Ky. Acts ch. 155, sec. 83, effective June 17, 1978. -- Created 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 354, sec. 15.
